          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Soft florals unfold into a warm, refined depth—effortless, expressive, and quietly captivating. Crafted for those who appreciate subtle luxury over loud statements, this is a scent that stays close, yet leaves a lasting impression. From polished mornings to candlelit evenings, it transitions seamlessly—never overpowering, always present. A modern take on oud, designed for everyday elegance.</p>",
